entry.value: SELECT ROW_NUMBER() over(ORDER BY AirportCode) as AirportId, AirportCode, AirportName FROM (SELECT DISTINCT (AirportCode), AirportName FROM FLOWFILE WHERE AirportCode IS NOT NULL)

SELECT m.ClaimNumber, m.DateReceived, m.IncidentDate, AirportId, m.AirlineName, m.ClaimType, m.ClaimSite, m.Item, m.ClaimAmount, m.Status, m.CloseAmount, m.Disposition FROM FLOWFILE m INNER JOIN ( SELECT ROW_NUMBER() over(ORDER BY AirportCode) as AirportId, AirportCode FROM (SELECT DISTINCT (AirportCode) FROM FLOWFILE a WHERE AirportCode IS NOT NULL) ) airport ON (airport.AirportCode = m.AirportCode)
